0"><ph name="&lt;ph class=&quot;- topic/ph &quot; conref=&quot;en-us_topic_0000001645659009.xml#ph122067484595&quot; id=&quot;ph1959151418587&quot; idp:conrefpath=&quot;200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000001596019118#EN-US_TOPIC_0000001645659009&quot; idp:userph=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;" word-end="false">&lt;ph id="f0"&gt;</ph><props><value key="prefix"></value><value key="localName">ph</value><value key="namespaces"></value><value key="isEmptyElement">False</value><value key="nodeType">Element</value><value key="displayText">&lt;ph class="- topic/ph " conref="en-us_topic_0000001645659009.xml#ph122067484595" id="ph1959151418587" idp:conrefpath="200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000001596019118#EN-US_TOPIC_0000001645659009" idp:userph="true"/&gt;</value><value key="hasDisplayText">True</value><value key="attribute:id">f0</value></props></tag><tag id="1"><ph name="&lt;uicontrol class=&quot;+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol &quot; id=&quot;uicontrol1891019245456&quot; conref=&quot;en-us_topic_0000207784470567.xml#438333&quot; idp:conrefpath=&quot;200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000002298266790#EN-US_TOPIC_0000207784470567&quot;/&gt;" word-end="false">&lt;ph id="f0"&gt;</ph><props><value key="prefix"></value><value key="localName">ph</value><value key="namespaces"></value><value key="isEmptyElement">False</value><value key="nodeType">Element</value><value key="displayText">&lt;uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " id="uicontrol1891019245456" conref="en-us_topic_0000207784470567.xml#438333" idp:conrefpath="200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000002298266790#EN-US_TOPIC_0000207784470567"/&gt;</value><value key="hasDisplayText">True</value><value key="attribute:id">f0</value></props></tag><tag id="2"><ph name="&lt;uicontrol class=&quot;+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol &quot; id=&quot;uicontrol158810276493&quot; conref=&quot;en-us_topic_0000207784470567.xml#438333&quot; idp:conrefpath=&quot;200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000002298266790#EN-US_TOPIC_0000207784470567&quot;/&gt;" word-end="false">&lt;ph id="f0"&gt;</ph><props><value key="prefix"></value><value key="localName">ph</value><value key="namespaces"></value><value key="isEmptyElement">False</value><value key="nodeType">Element</value><value key="displayText">&lt;uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " id="uicontrol158810276493" conref="en-us_topic_0000207784470567.xml#438333" idp:conrefpath="200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000002298266790#EN-US_TOPIC_0000207784470567"/&gt;</value><value key="hasDisplayText">True</value><value key="attribute:id">f0</value></props></tag></tag-defs></header><body><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c5e8a6b4-2d72-4c70-9477-b6bc35d4ab60"><source>Why Does the Battery Not Supply Power at Night?</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Does the Battery Not Supply Power at Night?</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1" /></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="vqABORKB+GISh+sagtgFWAd1rsY=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">vqABORKB+GISh+sagtgFWAd1rsY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="5820f1d0-af12-4a5c-8e27-27581f0902ca"><source>Intelligent scheduling policy (economic optimization)</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Intelligent scheduling policy (economic optimization)</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2" /></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="qcdCUbtcmuNagBeabFy/xQTJ8Xc=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">qcdCUbtcmuNagBeabFy/xQTJ8Xc=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="ad0fcc22-e3ea-462a-b163-24123d293200"><source>If the <x id="0" /> is enabled, the system dynamically adjusts the battery behavior based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">If the <x id="0" /> is enabled, the system dynamically adjusts the battery behavior based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">If the <x id="0" /> is enabled, the system dynamically adjusts the battery behavior based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">BcPkEXZarXA06t1vmUxopXTiFak=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d20abce2-a028-4e23-8ffb-ffbbeb25d6e7"><source>Nighttime is usually a low electricity price period.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Nighttime is usually a low electricity price period.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Nighttime is usually a low electricity price period.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">jAAidvrokQHkO9fatYqCxELjmDY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="11700ffc-dc70-4013-a490-2671865791f1"><source>During this time, the battery is preferentially charged (from the grid or PV system) instead of discharging, so that it can release electricity during high electricity price periods in the daytime to obtain higher returns.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">During this time, the battery is preferentially charged (from the grid or PV system) instead of discharging, so that it can release electricity during high electricity price periods in the daytime to obtain higher returns.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">During this time, the battery is preferentially charged (from the grid or PV system) instead of discharging, so that it can release electricity during high electricity price periods in the daytime to obtain higher returns.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">CHj5X9oc3JMsh+JbKjtT/84uzJw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d5b4dedd-66a6-4369-9e7e-ce4eaaeaf125"><source>Economic optimization (low-charging and high-discharging)</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Economic optimization (low-charging and high-discharging)</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Economic optimization (low-charging and high-discharging)</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">8QJCpWTz6WmOKDccTZz5o7eEHqo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="6c3bd0e6-a004-479d-80bd-2729c474f2e1"><source>The system implements arbitrage by charging at low electricity prices and discharging at high electricity prices.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">The system implements arbitrage by charging at low electricity prices and discharging at high electricity prices.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">The system implements arbitrage by charging at low electricity prices and discharging at high electricity prices.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Zpkfd5rLSXYwhegrLT1XlWk5blk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="00695111-f50f-4d4e-92ff-87a67880e743"><source>The energy charged at night is reserved for discharge during high electricity price periods the next day to maximize returns.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">The energy charged at night is reserved for discharge during high electricity price periods the next day to maximize returns.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">The energy charged at night is reserved for discharge during high electricity price periods the next day to maximize returns.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">wmFqDP3XtkM4rAv76Z9QHdnP0FQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="708507ad-7f04-42d1-8f08-842646297e69"><source>If the battery discharges at night, the opportunity for higher electricity prices during the day may be missed.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">If the battery discharges at night, the opportunity for higher electricity prices during the day may be missed.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">If the battery discharges at night, the opportunity for higher electricity prices during the day may be missed.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">/39MQI2qeQBdqbvo/XyqHWo4nj8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="68fb19ac-f2ce-4d88-8834-e4210306f1c8"><source>Time period restrictions in <x id="1" /> mode</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Time period restrictions in <x id="1" /> mode</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Time period restrictions in <x id="1" /> mode</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">OJ3K+15THEb5bL0fZ/em6U8qGBk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="284d53b7-65b1-4ef4-8b5f-7f46dcd59136"><source>In <x id="2" /> mode, you need to manually set the discharge time period (for example, during high electricity price periods).</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">In <x id="2" /> mode, you need to manually set the discharge time period (for example, during high electricity price periods).</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">In <x id="2" /> mode, you need to manually set the discharge time period (for example, during high electricity price periods).</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">ZLxY9QfK+t5DvQzhX0yR/qdv5Sg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="dae68192-a6a2-4c1f-8f77-37148e3b4831"><source>If the discharge window is not configured at night, the battery does not discharge by default.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the discharge window is not configured at night, the battery does not discharge by default.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the discharge window is not configured at night, the battery does not discharge by default.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">KeezgaZqswqz46xc7+OPr3qWpaM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="14232b0e-658f-4c6c-8135-be3ca3fdca34"><source>Backup power SOC policy</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Backup power SOC policy</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">SOC back-upvoeding</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">TQ5MP4gTm9wXvgS/Ma0G6QygKJM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="84ff97f2-dbbe-4302-b2bc-e7dc36aedb91"><source>The system sets the backup power SOC (for example, 5% to 20%) to ensure the power supply capability in the event of a power outage.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">The system sets the backup power SOC (for example, 5% to 20%) to ensure the power supply capability in the event of a power outage.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">The system sets the backup power SOC (for example, 5% to 20%) to ensure the power supply capability in the event of a power outage.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">0FfBmp7Y0LknOBtmt0/3tW+rZJo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="97ec5d4d-ed69-4386-8c89-c01aedff2dfd"><source>If the SOC of the battery is lower than the end-of-discharge threshold at night, the system forcibly stops discharging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">If the SOC of the battery is lower than the end-of-discharge threshold at night, the system forcibly stops discharging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">If the SOC of the battery is lower than the end-of-discharge threshold at night, the system forcibly stops discharging.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="15" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">i1N809T6C92HHToeoCEbeu/386k=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>